title: Marketing and Biz Dev for NFT mining proposal
body: If the NFT liquidity mining proposal passes and we decide to go forward with this product line, I feel that we would need to act ASAP with getting the product ready and getting word out there that we are building it. My proposal is this: We can reach out to the NFT youtuber Cagyjan (Link to his channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCIraLfgEfUNT_O8_OCTPbXg ). I think he can help us with the details of the NFT world that we may not know and also what direction we could go after we decide that this is whats next for the Parachute DAO. He can get the ball rolling with exposure to a 50K sub channel, as well as with ideas for business development going forward as an advisor to the Parachute DAO given his experience in the NFT world. If this proposal passes, we would need to reach out to him and negotiate with him to see how much it would cost PAR to have him as our advisor on this new project.
choices: Need to talk to Cagy first
author: 0xaE8667Fa8F52B5d467609E45Ee3237F5a02A21E9
